Written evidence submitted by The Community Woodlands Association (CWA)default&#xa0;
defaultThe Community Woodlands Association
default (CWA) is very pleased to have the opportunity to submit a response to the open consultation on land reform in Scotland launched by the Scottish Affairs 
defaultCommittee in July 201
default3.
default We fully endorse the paper the Committee published to stimulate discussion “432
default:50 – toward a comprehensive land reform agenda” which 
defaultpresent
defaults a
defaultn excellent 
