defaultThis is accounted for under the 
default“Sustainable Forest Management” (SFM)
default budget heading
default which covers forest planning, timber operations, forest protection and maintenance (including deer management), management and development of the estate, and sufficient social and environmental activity to ensure continued UKWAS compliance.
